<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Document Review Update</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #2d3748;
      }
      ul {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #555555;
      }
      .reason-box {
        background: #f3f4f6;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Document Review Update</h1>

    <p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for submitting your application to MDMAT. We appreciate your interest in our services and look forward to assisting you.</p>

    <p>We have reviewed your <strong><%= @proof_type.titleize %></strong> document and need some additional information or clarification:</p>

    <div class="reason-box">
      <p><strong>Reason for Revision:</strong></p>
      <p><%= @rejection_reason %></p>
    </div>

    <% if @remaining_attempts > 0 %>
      <p>You have <strong><%= @remaining_attempts %> <%= 'attempt'.pluralize(@remaining_attempts) %></strong> to submit your revised document. You can submit your revised document by:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Logging into your account and uploading a new document</li>
        <li>Replying to this email with the document attached</li>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <p>Please note that this was your final attempt to submit this document. Your application (ID: <%= @application.id %>) has been archived. You are welcome to start a new application after <strong><%= @reapply_date %></strong>.</p>
    <% end %>

    <p>If you need assistance or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <%= mail_to "info@mdmat.org" %>.</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The MDMAT Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
